    "We excluded participants who did not complete the posttest or had technical problems, remaining with 187 participants for our analyses.",
    "Table 3 summarizes the demographic information per group.",
    "We did not find significant differences between the groups in terms of age (χ 2 (4) = 1.07, p =.90) or gender (χ 2 (8) = 7.49, p =.48) as indicated by a non-parametric Kruskal-Wallis test 10.",
    "The median time spent on the study was 70 minutes.",
    "Participants were paid 9£ per hour."
  ],
